From ad4574e919423d70c4b7c191090421da2f0d5c2e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 08:15:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add WPF DNS Changer app for Windows

Implements a native Windows DNS changer (C#/WPF, .NET 8) with a modern
dark UI:

- One-click apply / reset (automatic-DHCP) of DNS per network adapter
- Add, edit, delete unlimited custom DNS entries (persisted to %AppData%)
- Search and live "current DNS" display per adapter
- ~22 built-in presets (Cloudflare, Google, Quad9, OpenDNS, AdGuard,
  Quad-family variants, plus Iranian anti-sanction providers like Shecan,
  403.online, Electro, Begzar, etc.)
- Runs elevated via app.manifest; changes applied through netsh + flushdns
- GitHub Actions workflow builds a single-file win-x64 exe artifact

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
